GLOBAL_LATENCY_DESCRIPTION: change GLOBAL_LATENCY to your lowest usual ping
DISABLE_BACKSTAB_DESCRIPTION: disables backstab spoofing (spoofed backstab is much faster but will not turn camera)
DARK_RUNEBURST_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - setting it to true will chain Dark Herald(СТЯЖКА) -> Runeburst(ОТБЛЕСК ЛУННОГО СВЕТА). Can toggle with runeburst1 command.
RUNEBURST_KEY_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Key for Runeburst(ОТБЛЕСК ЛУННОГО СВЕТА), find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
DREAMSLASH_LOCK_DESCRIPTION: Improves dreamslash stability at high ping, but you lose the ability to cancel dreamslash.
SHINING_DOUBLEHIT_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - setting it to true will autochain shining(НОВОЛУНИЕ) crescent second hit.
SHINING_KEY_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Key for Shining(НОВОЛУНИЕ) Crescent, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
SHINING_LOCK_DESCRIPTION: Shining delay lock, second hit cannot be used within this period.
SHINING_LOCK_DURATION_DESCRIPTION: Shining delay lock, second hit cannot be used within this period.
LEAPSLASH_INTO_GROUNDBASH_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - setting it to true will chain Leap Slash(импульс) -> Ground Bash(воля).
GROUNDBASH_KEY_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Key for Ground Bash(воля), find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
GF_X_DESCRIPTION: Auto use X_KEY when Godsfall(ПОСЛЕДНЯЯ ПЕСНЯ) is used. X_KEY must be set. This macro does not work without ROBOTJS.
RAGNAROK_X_DESCRIPTION: Auto use X_KEY(ВСЕ что вы туда поставите(кнопки z y x, пиво брошку и т.п) when Ragnarok is used. X_KEY must be set. This macro does not work without ROBOTJS.
X_KEY_DESCRIPTION: X Key. Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Y_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Y Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Z_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Z Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
SHINING_GUNGNIR_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - setting it to true will autochain gungnir after first shiny hit.
GUNGNIR_KEY_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Key for Gungnir Bite, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
